Let’s just say #Suspiria....didn’t.

name: Jasmine Evaristo
content: Alright, #SUSPIRIA: sweeping beauty and brutality; cathartic and revolting; angry and ravenous. A truly unsettling and visceral experience in the best way. Damien Jalet's choreography is primal. The dance sequences were thrilling and dreadful.
